[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Can you turn this into an ai agent and agentic code skill for xlaude code and then make an interactive app i can add to my other apps Got it. To deliver this, I need a few specifics so I don’t build the wrong thing. Please answer these (short answers are fine): What exactly is “this” you want turned into an AI agent? Paste the content/spec or link to it. Where will the “interactive app” live? Options: Web app, Shopify embedded app, browser extension, internal tool, or other. What should the app do (core user flows)? Example: “Input X → agent processes → output Y + actions Z.” Do you want the app to be: Standalone (own URL) Embeddable widget (iframe/script) Both Tech preference (if any): React / Next.js / Shopify App / Bubble / Webflow / Other Once you answer, I’ll: Convert your spec into an Xlaude agent + agentic code skill Build a live interactive app you can embed Provide a click-by-click SOP in a detailed table (with input/output + rationale) Create a Knowledge Base doc for this chat and keep it updated as we iterate I clicked on the genspark chat for the shopify manager. Can you access that Using Tool | Hub Session Searching for: shopify manager genspark chat View I can access prior Hub sessions, but I need the exact session. From the Hub, I see these related sessions (pick one): f891533d-d869-4b74-b458-6d51fd6504d3 — “I need to create a collection” d893f417-6f3f-4683-9b8c-053dd132b299 — “Diverse Lifestyle Hero Images…” 821227f0-b304-4a1a-96cf-827a4a3ed58a — “Contrast Visibility Fix” 8a8332c1-6fce-4e45-8b6a-269e21a269a8 — “Brand Resource Vault” Reply with the session ID you want me to open. AI Developer Your first AI employee Free Now GPT-5.2 Codex Speak AI Developer Shopify Preview File Explorer GitHub Scripts Skills Shopify Store Configuration Create Voice Agent + Add Store Add Shopify Store 1 Store URL Admin API Token Save API Key How to Get Your Shopify API Tokens 1 Install QuickToken App Search for 'QuickToken' in the Shopify App Store and install it to your store. Install QuickToken 2 Get Your Shopify Info Open QuickToken from your Shopify admin. Your Store URL and Access Token are displayed on the homepage. Copy and paste them into the form above."}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Source: "},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=daedc358-4f07-4b2b-8bf3-b6d35b3eed61&hub_id=fa240d79-dd2a-480e-84b6-0b968d46ab60","children":[{"text":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=daedc358-4f07-4b2b-8bf3-b6d35b3eed61&hub_id=fa240d79-dd2a-480e-84b6-0b968d46ab60"}]}]}]
